query:
SELECT at.id, at.auditName, at.auditCategory, atem.id as templateId, atem.templateName 
FROM auditTypes at 
LEFT JOIN auditTemplates atem ON at.id = atem.auditTypeId AND atem.isActive = 1
WHERE at.auditName LIKE '%daily%' OR at.auditName LIKE '%Daily%'
LIMIT 10;
